<H3> <TI>   Paris Club Talks `Ended With Complete Success' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Paris Club Talks `Ended With Complete Success' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1404071494 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 0500 
GMT 14 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1404071494 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia Khorizont Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Bulgarian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] I would first like to remind our listeners that we 
are awaiting confirmation of a piece of news that we received 
from a source close to the Government Commission on the foreign 
debt negotiations, namely that late last night, at 0130 in the 
French capital, the talks with the Paris Club of official 
creditors ended with complete success. According to the same 
source, an formula was agreed for rescheduling repayments of the 
debt for 11 years, with a seven-year gratis period. 

</TEXT>

