<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Serbian aggressor today again violated the 
cease-fire agreement in the (?Sarajevo) area. 
  [Correspondent] Shortly before 1800, the residents of 
Sarajevo were disturbed by powerful explosions in the area 
around Vrbanja Most. This was yet another provocative (?attack) 
by the chetniks, who used small arms and then fired several 
cumulative [kumulativan] mortar shells at the defense lines from 
the temporarily occupied territory of Grbavica. This marks the 
continuations of attacks by the aggressor, who attacked the 
[word indistinct] areas with mortars from its positions in [word 
indistinct] Dol [passage indistinct]. 

