<H3> <TI>   Serbs Launch Attack on Brcko Municipality </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Serbs Launch Attack on Brcko Municipality </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1404141694 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 
1300 GMT 14 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1404141694 </F>
<F P=104>  Zagreb Radio Croatia Network </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] This morning, in an attempt to widen the corridor 
through Bosanska Posavina, the Serbs again launched a heavy 
artillery and infantry attack on the free territory of Brcko 
municipality. Over 400 tank, howitzer, and mortar shells have 
landed on the Croatian village of (Bodariste). All the lines 
jointly held by members of the Croat Defense Council [HVO] and 
the Bosnia-Herzegovina Army were also pounded. 
  Three infantry forays were attempted during these attacks, 
during which two HVO soldiers were killed and six wounded. 

</TEXT>

